title: QUIZ: How Well Do You Remember “Reply 1994”?
text:
Pin   
Set in the 90s like its predecessor, “Reply 1997,”“ Reply 1994 ” takes us back in time and reminds us of a different time while following a dynamic storyline, trying to figure out who the husband is. Take this quiz to find out how well you remember the 2013 hit K-drama!
